last_episode_to_air.name: Enter the Bunny
last_episode_to_air.overview: Vincent draws a rabbit with his pen on a notebook, and tries many ways to make fun of the bunny. The bunny fights back and Vincent gets that this is a talented Kung Fu Bunny! Then Vincent draws a dog to help catch the bunny, however they fail. At the end Kung Fu Bunny jumps out from the paper to the real world, now the funny story between Kung Fu Bunny, Choy Bao Doggy and Vincent will never end!
